Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,否则上帝会从你身边夺走它\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}God will take it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝坏吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}Is God bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝是公平的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}God is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你差点就抓到我了 是不是 小子?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}You almost got me, didn't you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的白发是从你那里还是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}Did I get my white hair from you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是妈妈那里继承的?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}or from Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈那里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}From your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法相信我们没有她的任何照片\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}I can't believe we don't have any pictures of her.
