Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能救你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}I could only save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她漂亮吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}Was she beautiful?
