Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}Like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我继承了多少?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}How many did I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,全部\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那我今天要去镇上 对吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs15\fscx90\fscy80\b0}So I get to go to town today, right?
